      "content": "a counselor isn't gonna do anything. they don't get it. it's not just \"anxiety\", it's like... the whole world is just one big room of people waiting for me to fail so they can mock me. i can't even breathe without feeling like i'm being watched. it feels like i'm trapped in a nightmare that never ends. how am i supposed to just \"process\" that? it's constant.",
